name: Vintage Embroidery Shoulder Handbags And Totebags
description:
Features:
- Style: shoulder, cross, handbags, backpack, book bag, laptop bags, multi usage.
- Color: black with multi color sequins and embroidery.
- Material: thick and firm canvas, cotton lining.
- Outside: handmade Hmong beading.
- Opening: zippered top closure.
- Internal: a zipper pockets, a phone pocket, a wallet pocket.
- Approximate size: 37 x 60cm.

My design inspiration comes from the traditional Miao culture. I combine the luxury and elegant Hmong embroidery with the modern considerate design to create unique products.

All the bags appear with an ethnic characteristic, high quality and fashionable, utility style.

All of the bags are multi usage (see the detail in the picture). It can be widely used in various places and occasions such as office, school or parties.

We guarantee all the products are original designed, handmade with Hmong embroidery, the same as shown in the picture.

They are unique bags for the unique person.

My bag is original handmade and please allow some differences in the measurement. I describe and photograph items as accurately and honestly as possible.
